uk.ac.ebi.pride.utilities.data.controller.access

Interface QuantDataAccess

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DataAccessController
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDataAccessController, CachedDataAccessController, MzDataControllerImpl, MzIdentMLControllerImpl, MzMLControllerImpl, MzTabControllerImpl, MzXmlControllerImpl, PeakControllerImpl, PrideXmlControllerImpl, ReferencedIdentificationController

    public interface QuantDataAccess
    QuantDataAccess defines methods for accessing quantitative proteomics data

    Author:
    Rui Wang, Yasset Perez-Riverol
